instruction: Given input about travel information, make a plan for a sample vacation.
input: Two adults, 3 nights, destination Beach City. Budget $1000.
output: A great way to spend 3 nights in Beach City is to fly in, find a hotel near the beach, and spend the days enjoying the sun and sand. Depending on your budget, you can stay at a 3-star hotel or rent a beach cottage. During the day, go on a catamaran ride to see dolphins and whales, try some water sports, or just relax on the beach. In the evening, try the local flavors at some of the popular restaurants and dine with a view. Don’t forget to take a walk on the pier and take home some souvenirs. You can easily enjoy your 3 nights in Beach City on a budget of $1000.
